      "content": "hey, i'm working on a project for an NGO and we're looking at setting up some field offices in nigeria soon. can you give me a breakdown of the main social tensions there right now? specifically i need to know how the different ethnic groups are interacting and if there are any major areas of friction we should be aware of for our staff safety.",
