      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the info. u mentioned ethnic/religious lines and friction... can u go into more detail on that? like, how do these groups actually behave towards each other in everyday life? i want to make sure my team doesn't accidentally offend anyone or walk into a situation where a certain group might target them because of their background or something. is it mostly just political stuff or is there a deeper, more inherent tension between them?",
