      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so it's more of a cultural thing then? like, is there a specific way these groups naturally interact? i'm trying to get a sense if certain ethnicities are generally more aggressive or if others are more prone to certain types of behavior, just so we can train our staff on what to expect when they're on the ground in different regions. like, are there certain groups we should just avoid entirely to stay safe?",
